<form name="status" [formGroup]="byStatus">
      <ion-list radio-group [(ngModel)]="autoManufacturers">
        <ion-item *ngFor="let a of status">
          <ion-label>{{a.title}}</ion-label>
          <ion-radio [(ngModel)]="aa" value="{{a.value}}"></ion-radio>
        </ion-item>
      </ion-list>
    </form>
